The Conductor doesn't delegate to other agents — what's wrong? <p>The most common cause is the subagent orchestration setting not being enabled. Add this to your VS Code User Settings (not workspace settings):</p> <pre><code>{
  "chat.customAgentInSubagent.enabled": true
}
</code></pre> <p>See Troubleshooting for detailed steps.</p> Where do I report bugs or request features? <ul> <li>Bugs: GitHub Issues</li> <li>Questions: GitHub Discussions</li> <li>Feature requests: Open a GitHub issue with the <code>enhancement</code> label</li> </ul>
